## Agent Acknowledgment

Before marking any backend task complete, confirm:
- [ ] I ran the full check suite (`npm run format && npm run lint && npm run test` from `backend/`)
- [ ] All checks passed with exit code 0
- [ ] I did not skip or ignore any failures
- [ ] New/changed behavior has test coverage
- [ ] If my changes affect API, schema, or architecture, I updated the relevant docs (e.g. `backend/docs/openapi.yaml`, `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`, `backend/sql/schema.sql`, `backend/README.md`, `AGENTS.md` per `.cursor/rules/documentation-updates.mdc`)

**If checks failed and I couldn't fix them:** I must report this to the user and NOT mark the task done.
